# Microsoft Server 2012 Web Server Deployment - Practical Guide

## 🎯 Project Overview

This repository contains comprehensive practical materials for deploying web applications on Microsoft Windows Server 2012 using Internet Information Services (IIS). The guide includes step-by-step instructions, sample code, and troubleshooting resources specifically designed for IT training and educational purposes.
