### Web Development Understanding
- Comprehend the relationship between HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
- Understand responsive web design principles
- Learn modern web layout techniques
- Gain experience with professional web development practices

### Server Administration
- Configure Windows Server roles and features
- Manage IIS applications and application pools
- Implement basic security measures
- Monitor and maintain web server performance

